<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Whatsoeer" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Whatsoe'er,</orth> 1) == whatever: <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.216" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 216</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.108" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 108</bibl> (Qq <emph>whatsoever</emph>). <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.128" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 128</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 54</bibl>.<lb />2) == whoever: <cit><quote>rude companion, w. thou be,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.10.33" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 10, 33</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to doom the offenders, w. they be,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 3.4.67" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 4, 67</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>whosoe'er</emph>).
